node.text:
•

Dividends are a great dynamic that often gets overlooked when it comes to building wealth.
•

They can be used as cash flow, but also as a way to get the company to buy you more shares of itself.
•

Compounding power of dividends actually take your invested stocks to another level.
•

But also what’s unknown or not fully realized is that when the market is falling, good dividend Payer are still kicking out those profits to shareholders.
•

So it actually works in your favor.
•

Checkout this full video on my YouTube channel.
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW🏚⚖️🏚⚖️

node.text:
•

My brother @him500 & Myself Said we wanted to impact the culture in a way that’s never been done before.
•

We went to 7 cities in 7 days and packed out every venue.
•

But NEW YORK, New York by far was a battle ground. The crowd was fearless, and they was talking that ish.
•

Felt Like “The Tunnel” back in 98-99 (imma hip hop fan, I know all about it)
•

Every Gem dropped was challenged. Even to the point I laced them with stuff I’ve never talked about before.
•

Someone from the crowd said “Ion believe you, prove it Trap”.
•

I politely called him from the crowd, told him come to the stage & let him see the account with his own eyes and walked the crowd through the strategy I used.
•

It was at that moment, the crowd shafted and was like “We f’n With Trap!
•

My brother @him500 had to do the same thing, showed the crowd a year to date account on the same business plays his was giving them for free.
•

New York made us take off the gloves and fight. But it also showed them, We Ain’t No internet dudes.
•

Every play we gave, was plays we used on a daily.
•

Where I’m From RESPECT IS EARNED NOT GIVEN. And I’d rather it no better way.
•

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW🏚⚖️🏚⚖️

node.text:
Information ones from many different sources.

Ignorance is the absence of Truth!

Knowledge is the accumulation of Truth!

Understanding is the assimilation of Truth

Wisdom is the application of Truth!

Foolishness is the abandonment of Truth!

Don’t miss out on information that could change your life because it’s in the mouth of a person you may not agree with.

Blessings often times come in disguise!

The objective is to win the game, you ain’t gottta like the players!!

Big Trap⚖️🏚⚖️⚖️🏚

node.title: If the information will change your life, use it!!

APPRECIATE THE LOVE YALL SHOWED..

WALLSTREET LOOKS LIKE US NOW!!!

node.text:
Certain Situtaion Hit Real Different!!
•

My brother @_thr33_d been rocking with me since 1999. IN THE TRENCHES FOR REAL.
•

I was fighting attempt murder, he was fighting a body.
•

We both did stretches as kids for those crimes. And now we are first generation wealth builders.
•

He’s been rocking with me since i was selling t-shirts.
•

To see his excitement just on my lives, in my group. Even when we on the phone he telling everybody about stocks & how we gotta get out the streets.
•

when i told him he rocking with me at Investfest he was geeked. I just watched him move. He pulled up @rashadbilal @troymillings @themasterinvestor & let everyone know how they changed his life.
•

Like, for me, it’s truly about putting my guys in situations & in rooms  and letting them see there’s more to life than the streets.
•

And, that all that shit we dreamed of is  possible.
•

He said mannnn @investfestival was different slime, he ran up on jim jones he been on 100 since day 1 & i love it.
•

Because where we from, all we know is funerals & getting it out the mud.. This was new life for him.

•

I just smiled.. He stood at my booth & got in the mix and sold merch. Loyalty is priceless!
•

The goal is to breath life into the community & show them it’s possible.
•

I see it in his eyes that he sees the world different.
•

LOVE YOU slime🤞🏾⚖️🏚⚖️🏚 WALLSTREET PAYS US NOW!!!!!
